Q2/- What is the difference between an Application Server and a Web server?

   
   WebServer=>
   
   1) Java Based Web Server is the small\subset of the Application Server
   
   2) Web server contains only servlet container s\w.
   
   3) Web server communicate only http protocol.
   
   4)Web server is the light weight server s\w.
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   Application Server=>
                      
   1)Application Server contains both EJB and Servlet container s\w.
                       
   2)Application Server can be communicate any kind of protocol(Ex- http,smtp,ftp etc)
    
   3)Application server is a high weight server s\w.
   
   
   
   
   